title: Wood-style plank flooring, Elevator access, Controlled-entry access!
posting_body: ['Resort-style living gets a new meaning at Village on Main Apartments – located on the Point Ruston waterfront in Tacoma.', 'Enjoy a truly modern urban village experience with countless dining, shopping, and recreation options right outside your doorstep.', 'Not to mention the coveted amenities and unequaled interiors available to residents right within the community.', '-Move-in with NO SECURITY DEPOSIT:', 'Only a small one-time payment', '-Air conditioning with programmable remote thermostat                                                                                        Featured amenity', '-Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply)                                                                                    Photo                                                                                                                                 Featured amenity', '-Elevator access', '-Package locker with 24/7 access to packages', '-Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements', '-In-home washer and dryer                                                                                        Featured amenity', '-Panoramic views of South Puget Sound, the Olympic Mountains, and Mount Rainier', '-50 onsite retail with unique eateries and shopping right at your doorstep', '-Expansive bay windows with 2-inch wood blinds', '-Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance', '-Private balcony or patio                                                                                        Featured amenity', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Prices Change Daily', 'Flexible Lease Terms']
